<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-2D623085-6D07-4CA5-AD02-1096A05B8FE4" version="2" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-2D623085-6D07-4CA5-AD02-1096A05B8FE4" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install and configure TeamViewer 14</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-3971E95F-7900-4495-B02B-0182D686A815"><p class="- topic/p "> This document describes how to install and activate TeamViewer 14.
</p><p class="- topic/p "> It is important to know that the license that your organization has impact on the method of installing. 
</p><note class="- topic/note " id="GUID-06095CB1-591A-4C56-B0AC-9CF49F8FB5BC"><p class="- topic/p "> It can be that a VPN connection prevents a download, preferably switch of the VPN connection 
</p></note></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-4B4B7A7D-082E-4845-AA63-46A368E2545D" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Ask your local IT to what extend your license is valid for this version. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Installing without a license will result in a popup on the customer machine related to free trail use. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> In case the license need to be installed with Teamviewer 12; you need to first install TeamViewer 12. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See: 
<xref keyref="How_to_install_TeamViewer_12" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-6D15B772-91DC-411F-95E8-9CB75187818F.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text How to install TeamViewer 12 and Activate the License?>How to install TeamViewer 12 and Activate the License</xref> 
</p></li></ul></prereq><section id="GUID-10479CF3-8B8C-46D4-8704-CA4342C0AAA3" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Download procedure</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Click the link below to go to the download site of TeamViewer. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="https://www.teamviewer.com/en/download/windows/" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot gentext?>https://www.teamviewer.com/en/download/windows/</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Search or scroll down to a link indicating "<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">See previous versions</b>” and click on the link. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> See example given:
</p><fig id="GUID-3564D048-1793-4412-9D08-296BA49305DA" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F15C9BB1-03B5-49F2-86F2-769AB9ADED7F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F15C9BB1-03B5-49F2-86F2-769AB9ADED7F-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Browse to (or select) the section of TeamViewer version 14. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the version that matches your OS (typically: windows, x86-64bit /x86-32bit) 
</p><fig id="GUID-AD768C70-12E6-4832-A16F-23D89AD0DF19" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0A18D0E4-FD9C-4D94-AD72-B089136F6EEC-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0A18D0E4-FD9C-4D94-AD72-B089136F6EEC-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> By selecting the windows version, the installer of the TeamViewer application is downloaded to your laptop. 
</p></li></ol></section><section id="GUID-C6F5D82A-F632-438B-8744-791BB674167A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> installation procedure on windows</title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Go to the downloads section of your browser and double click the installer "<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">TeamViewer Setup</b>” to start the installation. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">In case a security warning popup is shown, click on “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Run</b>” to continue the installation. 
</p><fig id="GUID-5BDA44CA-D6C4-46B3-9C28-1FBC59AF38AC" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-AF073ED8-4B65-48E9-9489-64C9920687DD-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-AF073ED8-4B65-48E9-9489-64C9920687DD-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Click on "<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Basic installation</b>", if not already chosen. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If the bottom half of the window appears “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">How do you want to use TeamViewer?</b>” Click on “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Company / Commercial use</b> , check the box of "<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Show advanced settings</b>" then click on "<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Accept - finish</b>". 
</p><fig id="GUID-78EC1C03-C315-456C-8148-CD52DE2F5E23" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-AEB1FC14-039C-4034-8435-30A3346FB093-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-AEB1FC14-039C-4034-8435-30A3346FB093-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Depending on the organizational setting of your device a message could popup “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Do you want to allow this App to make changes to your device</b>”, optionally provide a login with a password. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Click “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Yes</b>”. 
</p><fig id="GUID-4BFCFA10-1838-4692-B2BF-0DE41FB77419" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-AEDC4D36-CF12-4E8E-A92B-8699D66BE446-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-AEDC4D36-CF12-4E8E-A92B-8699D66BE446-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> In the advanced settings check the “Use TeamViewer VPN” checkbox. 
</p><fig id="GUID-8EA50158-5285-4326-84C3-067667E2D429" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-59E34A2D-BF99-479D-8344-F45168BDF869-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-59E34A2D-BF99-479D-8344-F45168BDF869-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">TeamViewer will now begin installing…. 
</p><fig id="GUID-2D976AEB-026F-4B77-BE1E-980FF3EE4554" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1889B49B-953C-4260-9791-2C85F6D0B991-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1889B49B-953C-4260-9791-2C85F6D0B991-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">When completed, you should see this screen: 
</p><fig id="GUID-F8A677B3-513F-4AE7-B721-4E8C676BAE98" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4FE2E437-7100-4661-B121-A6B4FB516B54-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4FE2E437-7100-4661-B121-A6B4FB516B54-low.png"/></fig></li></ol></section><section id="GUID-A98361FA-8F44-4089-B67B-577D70A302A2" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> Additional Configuration</title><p class="- topic/p "> Depending on your organizational settings for your device it could be prohibited to make changes to your configuration. If possible; make the following additional changes.
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Click on “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Extras</b>” and in the drop-down menu, click on “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Options</b>”. 
</p><fig id="GUID-1CFFA15B-C04D-44D9-AA56-1A42EF0F586A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E300F58A-D72B-4E8D-A4FA-56C61EB0F363-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E300F58A-D72B-4E8D-A4FA-56C61EB0F363-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Now click on “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Advanced</b>” and then “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Show advanced options.</b>” 
</p><fig id="GUID-51375742-5F76-4A8C-A0AE-9F466194F148" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-33CFB42E-F6C3-4B99-8FEF-3018B4EBED2A-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-33CFB42E-F6C3-4B99-8FEF-3018B4EBED2A-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The below window will appear. 
</p><fig id="GUID-D15D990A-E62C-4296-A4D3-962A34160EF3" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FEE4937B-6DC5-4C1E-9440-D69C5989FD90-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FEE4937B-6DC5-4C1E-9440-D69C5989FD90-low.png"/></fig></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Change the settings for: 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">“<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Check for new version</b>” to “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Never</b>” and…. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">“<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Install new versions automatically</b>” to “<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">No automatic updates</b>.” 
</p><fig id="GUID-7E813B56-7631-4414-97B4-CAFC10D4A3CA" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DD7064FB-2928-42D6-96E1-BE75362A0DD8-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DD7064FB-2928-42D6-96E1-BE75362A0DD8-low.png"/></fig></li></ol></li></ol></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-DFD95E44-6FE2-4690-855D-446A64ABF90C.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>ORS: On Remote Service</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>